				origDataSource exch get 0()/SubFileDecode filter
				BitsPerComponent 8 idiv string/readstring cvx/pop cvx/putinterval cvx
				}for 
			]bind cvx
		}{origDataSource}ifelse 0()/SubFileDecode filter def		
	[
		origcolorSpaceElemCnt string
